---

<section class="ctx-section w-[80%] mx-auto  border-white/20 border">
  <div class="ctx-inner">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="ctx-header">
      <span class="ctx-badge">CONTEXTO · ANÁLISIS</span>
      <h2 class="ctx-title">Sobre los Datos y el Análisis</h2>
      <p class="ctx-subtitle">
        El Perú es una de las principales potencias mineras del planeta. Este análisis explora los
        <strong>3,055 sitios mineros</strong> registrados en el USGS Mineral Resources Data System (MRDS)
        para responder una pregunta central.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Central question -->
    <div class="ctx-question">
      <span class="ctx-question__label">Pregunta central</span>
      <p class="ctx-question__text">
        ¿Qué método de extracción domina en el Perú según el tipo de mineral y la región, y cómo se
        relaciona con la escala productiva y el estado de desarrollo?
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ctx-section {
    padding: 80px 0 60px;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .ctx-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  /* ── Header ── */
  .ctx-header {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .ctx-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.625rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--accent-lime);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(193, 214, 91, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(193, 214, 91, 0.15);
  }

  .ctx-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }

  .ctx-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ctx-subtitle strong {
    color: var(--accent-lime-light);
  }

  /* ── Central question ── */
  .ctx-question {
    padding: 24px 28px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-lime);
  }

  .ctx-question__label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--accent-lime);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .ctx-question__text {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Stats bar ── */
  .ctx-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .ctx-stats {
      flex-direction: row;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0;
    }
  }

  .ctx-stat {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ctx-stat__value {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent-lime);
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .ctx-stat__label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ctx-stat__divider {
    display: none;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .ctx-stat__divider {
      display: block;
      width: 1px;
      height: 36px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
  }

  /* ── Ranking cards ── */
  .ctx-rankings {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .ctx-rankings {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .ctx-rankings {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .ctx-rank-card {
    padding: 16px 12px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    text-align: center;
    transition:
      border-color 0.3s ease,
      transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .ctx-rank-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .ctx-rank-card__symbol {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent-lime);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .ctx-rank-card__name {
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.8px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .ctx-rank-card__row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ctx-rank-card__world,
  .ctx-rank-card__latam {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1px;
  }

  .ctx-rank-card__pos {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .ctx-rank-card__world .ctx-rank-card__pos {
    color: var(--accent-lime-light);
  }

  .ctx-rank-card__latam .ctx-rank-card__pos {
    color: var(--accent-brown-light);
  }

  .ctx-rank-card__scope {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  /* ── Method cards ── */
  .ctx-methods {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .ctx-methods {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .ctx-method-card {
    padding: 20px 18px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--method-color);
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ctx-method-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    border-top-color: var(--method-color);
  }

  .ctx-method-card__icon {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .ctx-method-card__name {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--method-color);
    margin: 0 0 2px;
  }

  .ctx-method-card__label {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 500;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .ctx-method-card__desc {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ── Analysis axes ── */
  .ctx-axes {
    padding: 24px 28px;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  }

  .ctx-axes__label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    color: var(--accent-lime);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .ctx-axes__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .ctx-axes__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .ctx-axes__grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .ctx-axis {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .ctx-axis__num {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent-lime);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .ctx-axis__title {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .ctx-axis__desc {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
</style>
